I’m not really sure what I wanted to say in this letter, but I felt like I needed to write. I guess you could say I’m the kind of person who writes a lot of letters to friends, so I figured it was bound to happen eventually. I’m honestly glad Ananya made me sit down and do it. It feels good to put my thoughts into words.

